\/span><\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e2810f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\" data-id=\\"2e2810f\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"text-editor.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">El gran crecimiento que hemos tenido luego la acogida que tuvimos con el servicio de limpieza en Lima, nos ha permitido tener colaboradores en otras regiones del Per\\u00fa.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-49ff089 elementor-widget elementor-widget-accordion\\" data-id=\\"49ff089\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"accordion.default\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<section id=\\"RECOMENDACIONES a tener en cuenta cuando contrates cualquier agencia de limpieza\\" class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-81324d1 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\\" data-id=\\"81324d1\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\" data-settings=\\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-row\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c4cdca elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\\" data-id=\\"5c4cdca\\" data-element_type=\\"column\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-wrap\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-c98b973 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\\" data-id=\\"c98b973\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"heading.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<h2 class=\\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\\" style=\\"text-align: center;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">RECOMENDACIONES A TENER EN CUENTA CUANDO CONTRATES CUALQUIER AGENCIA DE LIMPIEZA<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa09c26 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\" data-id=\\"aa09c26\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"text-editor.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Si no quieres contratar a PeruLimpio estas en todo tu derecho, sin embargo valora la posibilidad de delegar el trabajo de limpieza a gente capacitada y as\\u00ed aprovechar todos los beneficios de hacerlo (<strong>NO TE ARREPENTIR\\u00c1S NUNCA<\\/strong>).<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Aqu\\u00ed te damos algunas recomendaciones que puedes tener en cuenta antes de contratar los servicios de cualquier agencia de limpieza, lee por tu seguridad:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-04e82b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-accordion\\" data-id=\\"04e82b4\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"accordion.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion-item\\">\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"elementor-tab-title-5141\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-title elementor-active\\" data-tab=\\"1\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">CONTRATA UNA EMPRESA SERIA\\u200b<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<div id=\\"elementor-tab-content-5141\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix elementor-active\\" data-tab=\\"1\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Aseg\\u00farate de\\u00a0<strong>contratar una empresa seria,<\\/strong>\\u00a0respecto de los servicios que brinda; es decir, dentro de los servicios que pueda brindar,\\u00a0<em><strong>debe de especificar que incluye el servicio de limpieza<\\/strong><\\/em>, a fin de que no te des con la sorpresa de que ese servicio no inclu\\u00eda algunas partes de tu casa.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion-item\\">\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"elementor-tab-title-5143\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-title\\" data-tab=\\"3\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">CALIDAD DE LOS ACABADOS<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion-item\\">\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"elementor-tab-title-5144\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-title\\" data-tab=\\"4\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">TENER CUIDADO CON QUIEN ENTRE A TU CASA<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<section class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-e02b301 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section\\" data-id=\\"e02b301\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<section id=\\"precio\\" class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e9cbcd elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\\" data-id=\\"6e9cbcd\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\" data-settings=\\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"