ix elementor-active\\" data-tab=\\"1\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Aseg\\u00farate de\\u00a0<strong>contratar una empresa seria,<\\/strong>\\u00a0respecto de los servicios que brinda; es decir, dentro de los servicios que pueda brindar,\\u00a0<em><strong>debe de especificar que incluye el servicio de limpieza<\\/strong><\\/em>, a fin de que no te des con la sorpresa de que ese servicio no inclu\\u00eda algunas partes de tu casa.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion-item\\">\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"elementor-tab-title-5143\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-title\\" data-tab=\\"3\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">CALIDAD DE LOS ACABADOS<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-accordion-item\\">\\r\\n<h3 id=\\"elementor-tab-title-5144\\" class=\\"elementor-tab-title\\" data-tab=\\"4\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">TENER CUIDADO CON QUIEN ENTRE A TU CASA<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<section class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-e02b301 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section\\" data-id=\\"e02b301\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<section id=\\"precio\\" class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e9cbcd elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\\" data-id=\\"6e9cbcd\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\" data-settings=\\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"