pertos (<strong>sale m\\u00e1s barato<\\/strong>)<\\/span><\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<section class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bb4f82 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section\\" data-id=\\"6bb4f82\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-077f0d4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\" data-id=\\"077f0d4\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"text-editor.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Somos\\u00a0<strong>la mejor empresa<\\/strong>\\u00a0<strong>de servicios de limpieza<\\/strong>; contamos con colaboradores\\u00a0<strong>verificados<\\/strong>\\u00a0y altamente\\u00a0<strong>capacitados<\\/strong>. PeruLimpio, como empresa de servicios de limpieza es respaldada por nuestros propios clientes, debido a nuestra\\u00a0<strong>eficiencia<\\/strong>,\\u00a0<strong>rapidez<\\/strong>\\u00a0y\\u00a0<strong>experiencia.<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/section>\\r\\n<section id=\\"\\u00bfPOR QUE CONTRATAR UNA EMPRESA DE LIMPIEZA?\\" class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c26718 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-top-section\\" data-id=\\"0c26718\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-row\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-a8c2aad elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column\\" data-id=\\"a8c2aad\\" data-element_type=\\"column\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-wrap\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-d8065bc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\\" data-id=\\"d8065bc\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"heading.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<h2 class=\\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\\"><span style=\\"text-decoration: underline; font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\"><strong><em>\\u00bfPOR QUE CONTRATAR UNA EMPRESA DE LIMPIEZA?<\\/em><\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1a321e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\" data-id=\\"c1a321e\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"text-editor.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Por tanto,\\u00a0<strong>el servicio de limpieza es la soluci\\u00f3n<\\/strong>, por muchas razones:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<section class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-05b4534 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default elementor-section elementor-inner-section\\" data-id=\\"05b4534\\" data-element_type=\\"section\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-row\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-f6de4b9 elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column\\" data-id=\\"f6de4b9\\" data-element_type=\\"column\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-wrap\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-0bee39b elementor-view-stacked elementor-shape-circle elementor-position-top elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\\" data-id=\\"0bee39b\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"icon-box.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-icon-box-icon\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">\\u00a0<\\/span><\\/span>\\r\\n<table style=\\"height: 266px;\\" width=\\"1096\\">\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">BUEN MANTENIMIENTO<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">El correcto uso y aplicaci\\u00f3n de productos de limpieza\\u00a0<b>extienden la vida de los muebles<\\/b>, ello se logra si el personal de limpieza tiene experiencia y esta capacitado.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">AHORRA TIEMPO<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">Tenga en cuenta que el tiempo que usted dedica a la limpieza es un tiempo que puede aprovechar en otras actividades que le\\u00a0<b>generen ingresos o que lo hagan m\\u00e1s feliz<\\/b>.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">AHORRA DINERO<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">Muchos prefieren contratar empresas de limpieza\\u00a0PeruLimpio para reducir los costos, principalmente ahorrar tiempo que\\u00a0<b>siempre se traduce en dinero.<\\/b><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">GRAN CALIDAD DE VIDA<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">Los resultados del servicio de limpieza,\\u00a0<b>bien hecho<\\/b>, brinda un espacio limpio y reconfortable para nosotros, tambi\\u00e9n nos permite aprovechar todo el tiempo posible con nuestros seres queridos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">AMBIENTES BIEN LIMPIOS<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">La limpieza profunda y eficaz del servicio de limpieza,\\u00a0<b>brinda una mejor percepci\\u00f3n<\\/b>\\u00a0a nuestro publico, mejora nuestra imagen as\\u00ed como la nuestra empresa.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<td style=\\"width: 358px; text-align: center;\\">\\r\\n<h3 class=\\"elementor-icon-box-title\\">MEJORA TU SALUD<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\"elementor-icon-box-description\\">El trabajo de limpieza\\u00a0<b>bien hecho<\\/b>\\u00a0(siguiendo est\\u00e1ndares y utilizado insumos correctos) asegura\\u00a0<b>espacios libres de g\\u00e9rmenes<\\/b>\\u00a0que podr\\u00edan afectar a la salud y de vida de tus seres queridos.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-icon-box-content\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-27b2f55 elementor-column elementor-col-33 elementor-inner-column\\" data-id=\\"27b2f55\\" data-element_type=\\"column\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-wrap\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d9359a elementor-view-stacked elementor-shape-circle elementor-position-top elementor-vertical-align-top elementor-widget elementor-widget-icon-box\\" data-id=\\"1d9359a\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"icon-box.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-icon-box-wrapper\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-icon-box-icon\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sa