"5e00049\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"image.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-image\\"><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\"><img class=\\"attachment-large size-large\\" style=\\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\\" src=\\"https:\\/\\/serviciodelimpieza.pe\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/empresa-que-brinda-limpieza-a-casas.jpg\\" sizes=\\"(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px\\" srcset=\\"https:\\/\\/serviciodelimpieza.pe\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/empresa-que-brinda-limpieza-a-casas.jpg 728w, https:\\/\\/serviciodelimpieza.pe\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/09\\/empresa-que-brinda-limpieza-a-casas-300x169.jpg 300w\\" alt=\\"empresa que brinda limpieza a casas\\" width=\\"728\\" height=\\"410\\" \\/><\\/span><\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-image\\">\\u00a0<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-fba5763 elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column\\" data-id=\\"fba5763\\" data-element_type=\\"column\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-column-wrap  elementor-element-populated\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-wrap\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-element elementor-element-70b25d2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\\" data-id=\\"70b25d2\\" data-element_type=\\"widget\\" data-widget_type=\\"text-editor.default\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-widget-container\\">\\r\\n<div class=\\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\\">\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\"><strong>LIMPIEZA DE\\u00a0HOGAR\\u00a0<\\/strong>m\\u00e1s info aqu\\u00ed<\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n<p><span style=\\"font-family: ''comic sans ms'', sans-serif;\\">Ofrecemos un servicio integral, es decir el trabajo de limpieza de casas que ofrecemos incluye: el aseo de la sala, comedor, cocina, dormitorios, ba\\u00f1os, pas